text: The Ethiopian National Defense Force (ENDF) is the army of the country of Ethiopia. It is led by the Chief of the General Staff of Ethiopian army. The army of Ethiopia has existed for more than a hunderd years. However, its current form, the ENDF, has only been around since 1996. The number of soldiers is 162,000, about the same as country of Austria. The leader of the ENDF is Abiy Ahmed. Category:Military organizations Category:Government of Ethiopia
title: Ethiopian National Defense Force
